foods.description: CADBURY DOUBLE DECKER CHOCOLATE BAR 54,5 GR
foods.lowercaseDescription: cadbury double decker chocolate bar 54,5 gr
foods.ingredients: Ingredients: Sugar, glucose syrup, glucose-fructose syrup, vegetable fats (palm, sunflower, shea, rapeseed), WHEAT flour (with added calcium, iron, niacin and thiamin), cocoa butter, dried whole MILK, cocoa mass, dried skimmed MILK, fat-reduced cocoa, dried whey (from MILK), MILK fat, emulsifiers (E442, E471, SOYA lecithin, sunflower lecithin), dried EGG white, anti-caking agent (calcium carbonate), salt, BARLEY malt syrup, raising agent (ammonium bicarbonate), flavourings. MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 14% MINIMUM. CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN PEANUTS, NUTS.
